00:20:55,874 --> 00:20:56,928
(14 days before Mangzhong)

259
00:20:57,759 --> 00:21:02,279
We can't miss the hotpot in the capital.

260
00:21:03,319 --> 00:21:05,680
But eating it outside is ostentatious.

261
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:09,960
So I bought it. Let's enjoy it.

262
00:21:12,279 --> 00:21:14,160
How is your injury?

263
00:21:15,240 --> 00:21:19,200
- It's much better now. Don't worry.
- To you.

264
00:21:25,759 --> 00:21:29,480
Where can we find the Baohe Inn?

265
00:21:30,519 --> 00:21:33,720
I heard from Prince Qi that Men Sandao
has the Department look for it.

266
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:35,519
But there is still no clue.

267
00:21:35,519 --> 00:21:37,960
If he can't find anything,
what can we do?

268
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:42,519
If we can't find the place,
what about the thirty-year pact?

269
00:21:43,039 --> 00:21:47,240
I plan to find something
on the Discipline Seal.

270
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:50,839
You already have the Discipline Seal,
right?

271
00:21:50,839 --> 00:21:53,880
Yes, but it takes four seals
to open the treasure.

272
00:21:54,960 --> 00:21:58,000
I think the thirty-year pact

273
00:21:58,000 --> 00:22:00,519
is more important than the seal itself.

274
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:07,000
When the Disciplinary Department's chief
turned to the court,

275
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,279
he presented the seal.

276
00:22:08,279 --> 00:22:11,000
How could he
forget such an important clue?

277
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:12,559
So we have to look for his descendants.

278
00:22:15,279 --> 00:22:17,759
Huang Xing,
have you found his descendants?

279
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:21,839
When the Disciplinary Department's chief
turned to the court,

280
00:22:21,839 --> 00:22:22,920
he received some rewards.

281
00:22:23,640 --> 00:22:26,319
None of his descendants are officials.

282
00:22:26,319 --> 00:22:31,000
His son was a scholar, who once
was in charge of an academy in Jiangnan.

283
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:32,119
He has passed away now.

284
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:36,400
His grandson is currently teaching
in the Jiangzhe Region.

285
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:44,480
Bufan, the Southern Shaolin's inheritor
has become a school teacher.

286
00:22:48,484 --> 00:22:50,340
(Home)

287
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:05,480
Muqing, I've been busy
with the opening ceremony these days,

288
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:07,160
I've been very busy.

289
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:09,440
But I never forget to find the treasure.

290
00:23:09,960 --> 00:23:11,359
I've been thinking of the words

291
00:23:11,359 --> 00:23:13,599
on the burned wooden box.

292
00:23:14,119 --> 00:23:16,799
I made a guess
and I think it's reliable.

293
00:23:16,799 --> 00:23:18,680
So, I've come to share it with you.

294
00:23:19,359 --> 00:23:20,000
Tell me then.

295
00:23:20,759 --> 00:23:21,632
Firstly, the word of five.

296
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:27,920
Could it be referring to the time,
the fifth day of the fifth month?

297
00:23:27,920 --> 00:23:31,200
The word of Bao.
Could it refer to a place?

298
00:23:31,200 --> 00:23:35,640
For instance, Baota,
Baodian, Baozhai, and...

299
00:23:35,640 --> 00:23:39,039
Lin Haohan, you are very clever.

300
00:23:39,039 --> 00:23:40,279
It makes sense.

301
00:23:40,880 --> 00:23:44,279
I'm flattered,
but you're telling the truth.

302
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:47,319
Do you know about the Baohe Inn?

303
00:23:48,960 --> 00:23:53,440
Baohe Inn? The word of Bao?

304
00:23:54,480 --> 00:23:57,480
Muqing, have you figured it out?

305
00:23:58,480 --> 00:23:59,759
Come on. Let's talk about it.

306
00:24:05,079 --> 00:24:07,000
If you don't know about the Baohe Inn,

307
00:24:07,839 --> 00:24:09,599
we really have nothing to talk about.

308
00:24:12,240 --> 00:24:16,440
Muqing, you're hurting my feelings.

309
00:24:16,440 --> 00:24:17,880
You're not treating me as your buddy.

310
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:23,640
Buddy, if you don't know
about the Baohe Inn,

311
00:24:23,640 --> 00:24:26,079
it makes it hard for me
to think of you as a buddy.

312
00:24:28,799 --> 00:24:32,720
Even so, I still see you as my buddy.

313
00:24:33,319 --> 00:24:35,759
Even though you're breaking my heart,

314
00:24:35,759 --> 00:24:39,799
as your buddy,
I will tell you everything.

315
00:24:41,640 --> 00:24:42,839
You know the Baohe Inn?

316
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:46,559
So this is fate.

317
00:24:47,079 --> 00:24:48,920
If you ask others,
they probably don't know.

318
00:24:48,920 --> 00:24:52,319
But now, you've asked the right person.

319
00:24:55,680 --> 00:24:57,519
You really know?

320
00:24:59,519 --> 00:25:02,720
Muqing, have I ever deceived you?

321
00:25:02,720 --> 00:25:05,079
Have I ever boasted to you?

322
00:25:07,240 --> 00:25:07,960
You haven't.

323
00:25:08,519 --> 00:25:11,079
Buddy, come in and talk.

324
00:25:11,079 --> 00:25:11,880
That's more like it.

325
00:25:21,039 --> 00:25:23,839
From 1522 to 1566, in Fujian,

326
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:32,480
there was a large shop, Baohe Shop.

327
00:25:33,119 --> 00:25:36,200
Its business was extensive,
including an inn.

328
00:25:36,200 --> 00:25:40,079
The Baohe Inn is one of businesses
of the Baohe Shop.

329
00:25:44,799 --> 00:25:46,279
Buddy, go on.

330
00:25:47,119 --> 00:25:48,000
I'm done.

331
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:49,920
What?

332
00:25:49,920 --> 00:25:53,160
Yes, Baohe Inn,
the business of Baohe Shop.

333
00:25:53,160 --> 00:25:54,039
Where is it?

334
00:25:54,039 --> 00:25:55,880
What? How would I know?

335
00:25:55,880 --> 00:25:57,720
Didn't you say you knew where it was?

336
00:25:57,720 --> 00:26:00,032
You asked me if I knew the Baohe Inn.

337
00:26:00,032 --> 00:26:01,680
I know, and I have already told you.

338
00:26:02,279 --> 00:26:04,799
I have never stayed in that inn.
That was centuries ago.

339
00:26:04,799 --> 00:26:07,680
Even as an antiques dealer,
I don't know where it is.

340
00:26:10,119 --> 00:26:13,319
Can't you search for it?
I've already told you.

341
00:26:13,319 --> 00:26:16,119
Baohe Shop was a shop in Fujian.
Can't you find it?

342
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:21,240
It's been hundreds of years.
The inn might have changed its name.

343
00:26:21,240 --> 00:26:23,119
It's uncertain
whether it's still an inn now.

344
00:26:23,119 --> 00:26:24,599
But you can find out something, right?

345
00:26:25,440 --> 00:26:28,880
So I couldn't find it in any records
of the past two hundred years.

346
00:26:29,480 --> 00:26:30,759
Turns out that's a long time ago.

347
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:35,079
I'll have to take a trip to Fujian.

348
00:26:35,079 --> 00:26:36,160
You're going to Fujian?

349
00:26:37,119 --> 00:26:37,952
Are you going with me?

350
00:26:38,440 --> 00:26:40,000
You think I'm useful?

351
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:41,119
You're a lucky man.

352
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:46,240
You can't drive me away again.

353
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:47,279
Absolutely not.

354
00:26:47,279 --> 00:26:49,119
You can't stop me from getting benefits.

355
00:26:49,119 --> 00:26:49,920
You're allowed.

356
00:26:49,920 --> 00:26:50,759
Ten percent?

357
00:26:50,759 --> 00:26:52,039
No less than ten percent.

358
00:26:52,039 --> 00:26:55,359
Great, I will follow you to Fujian.

359
00:26:55,359 --> 00:26:58,920
I'll be at your service
and share the treasure with you.

360
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:02,640
Before that, I have to find out
where the Baohe Inn used to be

361
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:03,599
and its new name.

362
00:27:09,124 --> 00:27:10,784
(The 27th day of 4th month,
3th year of Xuantong era,)

363
00:27:10,784 --> 00:27:11,552
(13 days before Mangzhong)

364
00:27:19,716 --> 00:27:21,056
(Get)

365
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:50,640
How long will you be gone?

366
00:27:51,920 --> 00:27:53,599
It might take over ten days.

367
00:27:53,599 --> 00:27:56,279
Returning home to pay respects
to ancestors. It's a hassle.

368
00:27:58,400 --> 00:28:02,440
It's an act of filial piety.
How can it be a hassle?

369
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:09,200
Thank you. I will be back
before the tenth day.

370
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:15,960
No worries. Since you're going back,
take a longer rest.

371
00:28:16,799 --> 00:28:17,480
Thank you.

372
00:28:20,036 --> 00:28:21,720
(Get)

373
00:28:21,720 --> 00:28:23,160
Come again tonight.

374
00:28:29,599 --> 00:28:32,680
Zhuo Bufan has found some new clues.

375
00:28:34,319 --> 00:28:35,880
You need to hear from him
before you leave.

376
00:28:37,559 --> 00:28:38,200
Yes.

377
00:28:39,559 --> 00:28:43,960
(Get killed)
You may go. Come again in the evening.

378
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:49,680
Zhao Fu.

379
00:28:51,079 --> 00:28:51,840
Your Highness.

380
00:28:52,548 --> 00:28:57,920
Get Zhuo Bufan here tonight.
Do it secretly.

381
00:28:59,759 --> 00:29:00,400
Understood.

382
00:29:12,680 --> 00:29:15,440
The oil is hot.
Add green onion, ginger, and garlic.

383
00:29:18,200 --> 00:29:19,072
Good.

384
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:21,759
- Here you go.
- Sauce.

385
00:29:21,759 --> 00:29:22,519
Here come the eggs.

386
00:29:23,160 --> 00:29:24,000
Done.

387
00:29:25,079 --> 00:29:27,319
Alright, good.

388
00:29:27,319 --> 00:29:28,039
Cheers.

389
00:29:28,039 --> 00:29:30,079
Good wine and food.

390
00:29:30,079 --> 00:29:31,039
Try the dishes in a while.

391
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:40,160
Jialuo.

392
00:29:41,472 --> 00:29:42,359
Jialuo.

393
00:29:42,359 --> 00:29:43,079
What a surprise.

394
00:29:43,079 --> 00:29:45,440
Where have you been?
I couldn't find you.

395
00:29:46,599 --> 00:29:48,160
I thought you got lost.

396
00:29:48,160 --> 00:29:49,480
Right. Jialuo.

397
00:29:49,480 --> 00:29:52,079
You've missed so many delicious foods.

398
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:55,039
Mahua, big steamed buns,

399
00:29:55,039 --> 00:29:58,279
fish dumplings, and Hulatang.

400
00:30:01,480 --> 00:30:03,359
Who is that girl standing behind you?

401
00:30:04,319 --> 00:30:06,799
Come. This is the county magistrate.

402
00:30:07,799 --> 00:30:09,519
Greetings, sir.

403
00:30:09,519 --> 00:30:10,200
This is the Adviser.

404
00:30:11,039 --> 00:30:11,680
Greetings, sir.

405
00:30:11,680 --> 00:30:12,960
Nice to meet you.

406
00:30:12,960 --> 00:30:14,000
This is Mr. Xing who taught me.

407
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:16,160
We have met before.

408
00:30:17,279 --> 00:30:19,392
This is Mr. Wang, Mr. Li.

409
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:22,599
They are officers of Dagu County Yamen.

410
00:30:23,559 --> 00:30:25,319
Greetings to you all.

411
00:30:26,079 --> 00:30:29,319
What's wrong with you?
I'm asking who she is.

412
00:30:29,319 --> 00:30:31,640
You've introduced us all,
but who is she?

413
00:30:33,839 --> 00:30:37,000
She is Lin Anjing, the victim
of the Dagu murder case.

414
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:40,640
The nine people who were murdered
were her family and friends.

415
00:30:41,599 --> 00:30:43,759
Miss Lin and I are...

416
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:47,920
Miss Lin and I...

417
00:30:49,039 --> 00:30:50,519
Goodness, you're so slow.

418
00:30:50,519 --> 00:30:52,599
What are you to her?

419
00:30:52,599 --> 00:30:55,008
She and I...

420
00:30:55,008 --> 00:30:55,968
We...

421
00:30:56,920 --> 00:31:01,839
Sir, Jialuo and I have been together
these days.

422
00:31:03,599 --> 00:31:05,160
We have already committed.

423
00:31:06,200 --> 00:31:09,680
Jialuo brought me back to get married.

424
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:11,960
That's a good thing.

425
00:31:11,960 --> 00:31:12,559
Yes.

426
00:31:12,559 --> 00:31:14,240
- Good news.
- Great.

427
00:31:14,880 --> 00:31:17,039
You're of a marriageable age.

428
00:31:21,988 --> 00:31:25,824
(Zhou Jiaoqin, Wang Pengde)

429
00:31:27,972 --> 00:31:30,148
(Alcohol)

430
00:31:40,880 --> 00:31:42,880
Sir, this red cloth...

431
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:44,000
- Put it over her head.
- Okay.

432
00:31:46,559 --> 00:31:48,440
This is not necessary, right?

433
00:31:49,319 --> 00:31:51,680
You have already seen me.

434
00:31:51,680 --> 00:31:52,599
Yeah.

435
00:31:52,599 --> 00:31:53,319
Take it off.

436
00:31:53,319 --> 00:31:54,960
Take it off.

437
00:31:56,960 --> 00:32:00,640
Put it over and take it off.
Then enter the bridal chamber.

438
00:32:43,559 --> 00:32:46,599
Wang Jialuo, Lin Anjing,
it's your big day.

439
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:48,799
May you be happy and have a child soon.

440
00:32:49,400 --> 00:32:51,640
Wish you a happy marriage.

441
00:32:51,640 --> 00:32:52,880
Wish you a lovely life.

442
00:32:56,880 --> 00:32:58,119
Why are you silent?

443
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:01,799
I have already said to myself.

444
00:33:05,880 --> 00:33:07,640
After all, my father won't object.

445
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:16,680
Let's go. I'll take you
to see my master.

446
00:33:26,640 --> 00:33:31,000
How nice would it be
if we could live here?

447
00:33:32,279 --> 00:33:35,200
It's okay as long as you like
this small place of Dagu.

448
00:33:35,759 --> 00:33:38,920
I like this place. Really.

449
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:40,880
If we can live here,

450
00:33:41,480 --> 00:33:43,000
we won't have to think about anything.

451
00:33:43,559 --> 00:33:45,160
And we don't feel tired at all.

452
00:33:45,160 --> 00:33:46,240
Really?

453
00:33:46,960 --> 00:33:47,744
Yes.

454
00:33:51,400 --> 00:33:54,400
I promise you. After I catch Zhuo Bufan
to close the case

455
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:56,720
and protect the Altar Treasure
for the court, we will return.

456
00:33:57,480 --> 00:33:58,480
We live a good life here.

457
00:33:59,640 --> 00:34:01,920
After returning, I'll repair the house.

458
00:34:01,920 --> 00:34:04,440
So you can live in it happily.
By the way,

459
00:34:07,920 --> 00:34:09,024
it's the key to my house.

460
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:19,760
Whatever vegetables you want to eat,
I will plant them in the yard for you.

461
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:24,199
And if you want to eat meat,
I will raise pigs, chickens, and ducks.

462
00:34:25,880 --> 00:34:26,559
Jialuo.

463
00:34:29,039 --> 00:34:32,119
We just got married.
Let's stay at home today.

464
00:34:32,679 --> 00:34:34,079
Can we go back tomorrow?

465
00:34:34,599 --> 00:34:35,119
Okay.

466
00:35:18,440 --> 00:35:19,280
No progress?

467
00:35:21,079 --> 00:35:22,679
Yes.

468
00:35:22,679 --> 00:35:26,239
You've been in the capital for days
and even have gone to Tianjin.

469
00:35:26,239 --> 00:35:27,760
How could there be no progress?

470
00:35:30,039 --> 00:35:33,079
Zhuo Bufan got a clue from Prince Qi.

471
00:35:34,079 --> 00:35:38,800
He went to Tianjin to find a madman,
the inheritor of the Dharma Department.

472
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:41,960
I don't know if he's the inheritor,
but he is a madman for sure.

473
00:35:41,960 --> 00:35:43,079
Nothing was gained.

474
00:35:44,199 --> 00:35:46,199
I wish to gain something.

475
00:35:47,320 --> 00:35:50,199
But nothing was found in the end.

476
00:35:50,880 --> 00:35:51,960
Nothing else?

477
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:58,440
My nation used to be known
as the Wo state.

478
00:35:58,960 --> 00:36:02,119
Since the reign of Emperor Xuanzong,
our nation has been called Japan.

479
00:36:03,199 --> 00:36:07,119
We paid tribute yearly, and your nation
was known as the Celestial Empire.

480
00:36:07,880 --> 00:36:10,039
But after the Meiji Restoration,
things were different,

481
00:36:10,639 --> 00:36:12,160
because we know
the importance of change.

482
00:36:12,639 --> 00:36:16,039
I believe you're as far-sighted as us.

483
00:36:24,039 --> 00:36:27,480
I know some clues,
but I don't know if they're of any use.

484
00:36:28,119 --> 00:36:28,840
Tell me about it.

485
00:36:29,480 --> 00:36:33,880
The chief inheritors of the Southern
Shaolin meet once every 30 years.

486
00:36:34,760 --> 00:36:38,159
They meet in the Baohe Inn.

487
00:36:38,800 --> 00:36:42,239
They're supposed to meet
on the sixth day of next month.

488
00:36:43,519 --> 00:36:45,239
Such important information.

489
00:36:45,920 --> 00:36:49,360
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

490
00:36:49,360 --> 00:36:52,480
Three of the four inheritors are dead.

491
00:36:52,480 --> 00:36:54,360
What's the point of meeting again?

492
00:36:54,360 --> 00:36:56,559
And one of them is unknown.

493
00:36:56,559 --> 00:36:58,360
Who knows if he will show up?

494
00:37:02,679 --> 00:37:04,280
Sounds promising.

495
00:37:04,800 --> 00:37:07,159
I see no hope.

496
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:12,640
Zhuo Bufan never gave up
when hunting the treasure.

497
00:37:13,159 --> 00:37:15,519
Why do you see no hope?

498
00:37:17,719 --> 00:37:20,840
There are only a few days left
until the appointed day.

499
00:37:21,519 --> 00:37:24,039
No one knows where the Baohe Inn is.

500
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:28,079
We don't know,
and Men Sandao doesn't know either.

501
00:37:28,079 --> 00:37:29,519
Everyone is desperately searching.

502
00:37:31,159 --> 00:37:34,880
All of you can't find the place,

503
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:37,920
so they will miss this appointment?

504
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:43,719
Didn't Zhuo Bufan do something else?

505
00:37:43,719 --> 00:37:45,119
There's nothing he can do.

506
00:37:45,119 --> 00:37:46,639
He will do something, won't he?

507
00:37:48,599 --> 00:37:51,039
He'll find the inheritor's descendants
of the Disciplinary Department.

508
00:37:52,440 --> 00:37:55,719
That inheritor sided
with the court decades ago.

509
00:37:55,719 --> 00:37:57,719
What secrets could his descendants have?

510
00:37:57,719 --> 00:37:59,880
The court could know all of his secrets.

511
00:37:59,880 --> 00:38:02,639
Zhuo Bufan doesn't think so.
He wants to give it a try.

512
00:38:08,639 --> 00:38:12,239
Yes, if I were him, I would do the same.

513
00:38:13,079 --> 00:38:16,679
Alright, I have to go.
Staying too long would arouse suspicion.

514
00:38:17,239 --> 00:38:19,104
Go through the back door.
Someone will walk you out.

515
