530
00:39:34,960 --> 00:39:41,039
I know you'll go to the Baohe Inn
for the thirty-year pact.

531
00:39:46,079 --> 00:39:52,159
You ask for leave with a lame excuse.
Ancestor worship?

532
00:39:55,320 --> 00:39:58,880
I have always been careful
in employing people.

533
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:03,450
Your father's death anniversary
is in the 8th month,

534
00:40:03,450 --> 00:40:05,960
and your mother's is in the 1st month.

535
00:40:06,480 --> 00:40:11,000
