in the twelfth month.

536
00:40:11,000 --> 00:40:14,599
Since when do you pay respects
in the fifth month?

537
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:24,719
Yes, I put poison in the tea.

538
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:36,199
Look, when you asked for leave
this afternoon,

539
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:39,119
I wrote something for you.

540
00:40:41,599 --> 00:40:44,880
Get killed for stupid stuff.

541
00:40:46,840 --> 00:40:49,480
Get imprisoned for survival.

542
00:40:51,719 --> 00:40:57,039
No traitors can be loyal.

543
00:41:08,179 --> 00:41:11,251
♪Deep affection in the past♪

544
00:41:11,839 --> 00:41:15,059
♪Only then do I write to you
to say farewell♪

545
00:41:16,459 --> 00:41:21,011
♪In sorrow, I nearly lay down the pen♪

546
00:41:22,849 --> 00:41:25,747
